    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Space Station Adventure: No response from Mars!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Martian station is no longer transmitting! The Company sends an under-qualified, under-equipped technician to fix the problem. Will he carry the weight of the Super-Corporation's expectations alone?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the artificial intelligence of his personal computer and help him win the challenges that lie ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through several chapters filled with mini-games, develop the AI's personality, win the trust of your biological colleagues and guide them through this interactive adventure where your every decision can decide the fate of all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This multiple-choice story offers many twists and turns to avoid or follow, each with a different plot and a different ending!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive text game: experience the adventure through AI sensors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Numerous high-impact mini-games: failure sometimes opens new doors!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A non-linear story: there are many forks in your path, leading to a multitude of endings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wide range of development opportunities: will you become an indispensable application or a malicious AI? Will you overcome your biological colleagues' prejudices or betray their trust?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A human and poignant narrative experience!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take decisions for the AI and give good advice to your human technician.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras/4d8d9119975617401e69d78129066f14.avif?t=1735806805\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras_big/4d8d9119975617401e69d78129066f14.avif?t=1735806805 width=800 height=138 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with the environment or with technical elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras/8a4514c22799137840d15f8ebff916a7.avif?t=1735806805\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras_big/8a4514c22799137840d15f8ebff916a7.avif?t=1735806805 width=800 height=486 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Consult information in your database.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras/1d26cb57588681f2958d80a550db6deb.avif?t=1735806805\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras_big/1d26cb57588681f2958d80a550db6deb.avif?t=1735806805 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Return to certain points in the story using Checkpoints to test other paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras/684fd8f2b7418c8ace9be0a26adc5e86.avif?t=1735806805\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras_big/684fd8f2b7418c8ace9be0a26adc5e86.avif?t=1735806805 width=800 height=68 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A wealth of content</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 endings to discover, each with a multitude of variations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story of over 100,000 words</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >36 achievements to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No microtransactions, pay once for the full game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replay the story many times to discover all its secrets</p></li></ul>",
